<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="{locale()}">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>500 — Internal Server Error</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif; max-width: 640px; margin: 4rem auto; padding: 0 1rem; color: #333; text-align: center; }
        h1 { font-size: 4rem; color: #ccc; margin-bottom: 0; }
        p { color: #888; }
        a { color: #2d6a4f; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>500</h1>
    <p>Something went wrong on our end.</p>
    <a href="/">← Back to home</a>
</body>
</html>
